{
  "comment": "对 @forsion/tangu-agent 仅 import type(paths 指向本仓 types/ 类型契约,故可脱离核心仓库独立构建)。verbatimModuleSyntax=true 把任何【值导入】核心变成编译错误——P0 硬保证(插件绝不复制核心模块图)。运行时全走 ctx.sdk。`npm run build` 自包含,产出 dist/(已提交,供 Forsion Market 源码 zip 安装免构建)。",
  "compilerOptions": {
    "target": "ES2022",
    "module": "NodeNext",
    "moduleResolution": "NodeNext",
    "lib": ["ES2022"],
    "strict": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "verbatimModuleSyntax": true,
    "declaration": false,
    "sourceMap": true,
    "outDir": "./dist",
    "rootDir": "./src",
    "paths": {
      "@forsion/tangu-agent": ["./types/tangu-agent.d.ts"]
    }
  },
  "include": ["src/**/*"],
  "exclude": ["node_modules", "dist"]
}
